    ],
    "As a young scholar he made the acquaintance of the collector and art historian <a href=\"/mahond\">Denis Mahon</a> with whom he subsequently collaborated on several books.": [],
    "In 1971 Pepper wrote an article for the <em>Art Quarterly</em> on the psychological approach to Guido Reni, one of the artists on whom his fame would rest.": [],
    "In 1984 his monograph and <em>catalogue raisonn\u00e9</em> on the artist became the standard.": [],
